{"tid":1394254,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 承認非所有 Cores 都能達 Boost 時脈","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:14:45.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5727e6c745ac443eca81e226356ef38841ed03","tid":1394254,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"自 7 月份 AMD 正式發佈 Ryzen 3000 系列處理器之後，在不少地區包括香港在內都賣到斷貨，Ryzen 9 3900X、Ryzen 7 3700X、Ryzen 5 3600 三款型號可以話是「一 U 難求」，在全球都獲得極大的好評，不過，最新在外國發燒級玩家就表示，Ryzen 3000 系列並非所有的處理器的 All Cores 都能夠達到官方標榜 Boost 頻率。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/18212/Ryzen_3000_處理器性能存質疑_AMD_承認非所有_Core_都能達_Boost_時脈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F18212%2FRyzen_3000_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E5%AD%98%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91_AMD_%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89_Core_%E9%83%BD%E8%83%BD%E9%81%94_Boost_%E6%99%82%E8%84%88&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIESbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=0d61aaa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/18212/Ryzen_3000_處理器性能存質疑_AMD_承認非所有_Core_都能達_Boost_時脈</a>"},{"pid":"7fbee45821b8e3cf107d4e0f5bea09a5c41f1223","tid":1394254,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"排完隊仲要抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01051f75240f5fb5f85e401bba05ef3d07cde768","tid":1394254,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"基本上，不論是 Intel 還是 AMD 處理器都有提供兩個時脈速度：一個為「Base Clock」基礎時脈，這是代表處理器運行最基本的時脈，另一個就是「Boost Clock」加速時脈，這是處理器運行最高的速度，具體取決於某些任務、條件、熱量等因素，實際得出的性能變得更加複雜。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.gadgets360cdn.com/large/intel_9thgen_core_1556014565989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Fintel_9thgen_core_1556014565989.jpg&h=72c37f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Intel 的 CPU 在指定的運作環境下，保証可達最高時脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n然而，近日有不少的外國 PC 發燒友及 reddit 用戶抱怨，Ryzen 3000 系列處理器似乎無法完全達到官方標榜的 Boost 時脈，因此外媒 Tom's Hardware 特別深入作出研究，並得出了一些重要的發現，在其測試的 Ryzen 5 3600X 處理器上，只有一個核心達到了 4.4GHz 的 Boost 時脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/07/source/0721035131680482947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F07%2Fsource%2F0721035131680482947.jpg&h=6e53b93b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n再進行更深入的測試，Tom's Hardware 發現最快及最慢的核心之間存在大約 75MHz-100MHz 的差異，並且只有一個核心能夠達到分配的單核時脈提升。在宏觀來看，差異並不是很大，但對比上一代 Ryzen 處理器可以在所有內核上達到 Boost 時脈頻率，顯示了 AMD Zen 2 架構與 Zen/Zen+ 的 per-core 增壓性能相比，AMD 在新架構改進時出現了變化。"},{"pid":"92d7045e71f8dacb41619df6b45829582fa0adca","tid":1394254,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"AMD 官方就此作出回覆，承認一些 Ryzen 3000 處理器的內核比其他內核更快，另外，由於 Windows 10 Scheduler 為 AMD CPU 作出優化及最新驅動程式的改進，運行最新版本的 Windows 10 作業系統在使用快速及慢速核心方面相對較好，而使用舊版 Windows 作業系統因為無法有效地將線程安排到最快的內核中，從而導致 Ryzen 3000 系列處理器在某些工作負載中的時脈和性能降低，這亦是部份用家投訴的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/08/source/0115123959951790654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F08%2Fsource%2F0115123959951790654.jpg&h=80cda080&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nTom's Hardware 分析認為，這些較慢的內核可能是 Ryzen 3000 處理器在超頻方面不是特別有優勢的原因，因為較慢的內核可能難以維持更高的時脈，從而降低了處理器的整體超頻潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"5c969d3280539daa303490d73d8de25980acd252","tid":1394254,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fbee45821b8e3cf107d4e0f5bea09a5c41f1223","tid":1394254,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"排完隊仲要抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaVzfhc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaVzfhc.png&h=136ddb08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f4c3d4c10b977c5cb9755d3e7b96e144192ca85","tid":1394254,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c969d3280539daa303490d73d8de25980acd252","tid":1394254,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fbee45821b8e3cf107d4e0f5bea09a5c41f1223","tid":1394254,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"排完隊仲要抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaVzfhc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaVzfhc.png&h=136ddb08&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"盲粉"},{"pid":"261a724f69a9894f8982ac5e131b102acd349902","tid":1394254,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"腦海浮現《The Inkpot》嘅調子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfe873424f446b4d33816ed91113029d5ef9e75","tid":1394254,"uid":1123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"intel 都係all core 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非s 尾"},{"pid":"fe4055c75db960d29437f03788b4f262fca04439","tid":1394254,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"你唔用win10先有問題喎"},{"pid"